				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Don't close your mind to all the options... <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
I've also two boxed a bard (as well as a cleric and enchanter) with my Mage:
<br />

<br />
Pros
<br />
- Get there fast
<br />
- Lulls
<br />
- Mezzes
<br />
- Mana Song
<br />
- Tracking
<br />
- Snare
<br />
- Mana free DoT
<br />
Cons
<br />
- Repetative Stress Injuries
<br />

<br />
I three box an mage/enchanter/cleric right now, and it's an awesome combo.  The biggest thing I feel that hobbles me sometimes is lack of snare.  This really hurt me in GoD where mobs are tightly packed, MR is high and adds are truely dangerous.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://scrubfire.dyndns.org/KJ_Sig.jpg" border="0" />
