				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've used both a friends 65 cleric and my 56 shaman.  Either way you go you can't loose.  Since the cleric is a friends bot I don't get to use her much so I duo with my shaman nearly exclusivly.  I love using both.  I can tell you I certainly enjoy my pet being able to tank two slowed hobgoblins from PoN with maybe one heal to the pet during the fight.  The real trick with having a shaman is agro control, slowing a mob pulls a lot of agro.  With a cleric there is no agro when CH'ing a pet, so not much to worry about.
<br />

